---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const lastUpdated = 'April 2026';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Lou's Heating & Cooling"
  description="How Lou's Heating & Cooling collects, uses, and protects information from website visitors and customers."
  canonical="/privacy/"
>
  <section class="page-hero section-primary section-sm">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p>Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-narrow legal-copy">
      <p><em>This Privacy Policy is a placeholder pending finalized copy from the business owner. The site does not collect personal data beyond what is voluntarily submitted via the contact form.</em></p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>When you submit the contact form on this site, we collect the name, phone number, email address, requested service, and any details you choose to share about your HVAC issue. We may also collect basic technical data (the page you submitted from, your browser's user agent, and a hashed approximation of your IP address) to help reduce spam.</p>

      <h2>How We Use This Information</h2>
      <p>We use the information you submit to respond to your inquiry, schedule service, and follow up after the work is complete. We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information to third parties.</p>

      <h2>Service Providers</h2>
      <p>We use trusted third-party services to deliver our website and respond to inquiries:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Email delivery</strong> via Resend, which forwards your form submission to Lou directly.</li>
        <li><strong>Lead management</strong> via Housecall Pro, our scheduling and customer-management platform.</li>
        <li><strong>Database hosting</strong> via Supabase, where contact form submissions are recorded for follow-up.</li>
        <li><strong>Hosting and analytics</strong> via Netlify and Umami; basic, anonymized analytics about page visits help us improve the site.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>This site uses minimal, privacy-friendly analytics that do not require cookie consent banners. We do not use advertising cookies or third-party trackers.</p>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You can request that we delete the personal information you've submitted by emailing <a href="mailto:lousheatingcooling@icloud.com">lousheatingcooling@icloud.com</a>. We'll respond within a reasonable time.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about this Privacy Policy? Call <a href="tel:3039498584" class="phone-link">(303) 949-8584</a> or email <a href="mailto:lousheatingcooling@icloud.com">lousheatingcooling@icloud.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.legal-copy h2 { margin-top: var(--space-8); margin-bottom: var(--space-3); color: var(--color-primary); }
.legal-copy p, .legal-copy ul { color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.8; }
.legal-copy ul { padding-left: var(--space-5); }
.legal-copy li { margin-bottom: var(--space-2); }
.legal-copy a { color: var(--color-primary); }
.legal-copy em { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-style: italic; }
</style>
